      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, delivering 333hp through individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS variable valve timing. Mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain is robust and provides the tactile engagement purists demand. The chassis has been proactively maintained, including a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed trailing arm bushings to ensure structural rigidity. While the exterior displays honest patina consistent with its 'good' driver-grade status, the performance remains sharp thanks to the M Variable Differential Lock and a well-damped suspension setup. This is a technically sound machine for the driver who prioritizes engine harmonics and corner-exit traction.",
